1
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:57,000
How did you know it was me?

2
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,840
First is the smell.

3
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:05,480
Remember when we first found Sun Wuwei,

4
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,330
the smell of sesame cakes at his stall?

5
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:11,220
When we investigated Zhao Xuanli's case together,

6
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,560
the sesame cakes you brought us

7
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:15,160
had the same smell.

8
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:19,360
You've known Liu Shiqin since childhood.

9
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:22,060
When Liu Shiqin was pestered by Sun Wenhuai,

10
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,800
how could you not know his name?

11
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:37,000
This is the most common wooden box principle in street magic.

12
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,960
There are two layers inside.

13
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,120
The contents are different every time it's opened.

14
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,400
The antique desk you gave me,

15
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,960
its secret compartment

16
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,410
had been tampered with by you long ago.

17
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,200
That day,

18
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,240
using the topic of the strange tales

19
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,600
I found at the ghost market,

20
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,360
you pretended to rummage through the desk.

21
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,400
Taking this opportunity,

22
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:02,040
you let us find the couplet in the secret compartment.

23
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:04,240
You deliberately guided us to discuss the couplet,

24
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:07,360
but you had no idea how we would match the second line.

25
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,680
So,

26
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,080
Su Lang would get to it first.

27
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,800
At that time, I noticed a detail.

28
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,560
Su Lang's handwriting

29
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:18,000
matched the writing on the couplet.

30
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,480
Then,

31
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:22,960
under the pretext of Li Jinglan thinking of a better second line,

32
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,290
you opened the hidden compartment again.

33
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,520
I believe

34
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:30,600
you must have had another piece of rice paper on you at that time.

35
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:32,760
The couplet was already written on it,

36
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:35,890
along with the imitation of Sun Wenhuai's handwriting.

37
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,320
What was used here

38
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:40,520
is the principle of the hidden compartment in the wooden box.

39
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,280
As for the handwriting on the reply letter

40
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,960
that slowly appeared,

41
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,520
that used the silver salt development method.

42
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:50,200
Using salt water or liquid made from special substances

43
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,560
to write on the paper.

44
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,680
Once it dries,

45
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,320
the writing disappears.

46
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,480
But when baked over a candle,

47
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,440
the writing appears.

48
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,680
This letter,

49
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:10,240
I believe, was written by Sun Wenhuai himself.

50
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,490
Look closely at the last sentence.

51
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,840
"Su Yu'an

52
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:18,560
is the culprit who framed me.

53
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:23,320
I hope the court will investigate clearly."

54
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,280
If it were written to me,

55
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:30,080
why would he use the word 'court'?

56
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,840
I knew it.

57
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:40,200
I couldn't hide it from you in the end.

58
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,920
Indeed.

59
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,680
Back then, there was a blood letter

60
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,560
that Sun Wenhuai entrusted someone

61
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:52,560
to give to the young Sun Wuwei.

62
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,200
Fresh out of the pot.

63
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:59,810
Here's one for you, and I'll take one to taste.

64
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,500
Are there any hot ones?

65
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,680
The early bird catches the worm.

66
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,560
Get me a hot one.

67
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,240
I want the kind that burns my mouth.

68
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,160
You corrupt official!

69
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,640
You corrupt official! I'll kill you!

70
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,840
Don't do anything rash.

71
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,570
Please don't do anything rash.

72
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,760
Who are you?

73
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,330
I committed perjury back then,

74
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:28,940
insisting that Sun Wenhuai intentionally harmed Liu Shiqin,

75
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,160
which led to his wrongful imprisonment.

76
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,040
He gave his suicide note to his brother in prison.

77
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:38,200
However, by the time I saw that note,

78
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:41,480
Sun Wuwei had already returned from exile.

79
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,080
Do you still remember Sun Wenhuai?

80
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,600
Sun Wenhuai.

81
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,600
If this blood-written letter falls into the hands of the authorities,

82
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:53,330
I will certainly be dismissed and investigated.

83
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,280
Now,

84
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,600
I know the whole truth.

85
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:03,320
But I can't decide what to do.

86
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:07,080
I pleaded with Sun Wuwei to hide the truth for now,

87
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:09,720
promising to clear Sun Wenhuai's name.

88
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,080
I thought of a way.

89
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,880
Using the principles of street magic,

90
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,840
I made a special wooden table.

91
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,720
While you were moving,

92
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:22,520
I had Sun Wuwei and Su Lang carve an aged character "Wu,"

93
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:25,920
putting on a show of sending a message from the afterlife.

94
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:29,600
Seeing the two of you solve bizarre cases time and again,

95
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:32,000
I wanted to use your help

96
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,600
to clear Sun Wenhuai's name.

97
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:38,400
You led us to start from the case files

98
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,280
and find Liu Shiqin's autopsy report.

99
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:42,080
After following the clues to open the coffin,

100
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:44,480
the truth of the advisor's death surfaced.

101
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:49,320
All suspicions unexpectedly point to Chen You, an official.

102
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,490
Court is adjourned.

103
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,770
When the investigation hit a dead end,

104
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,800
you proposed

105
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:57,520
to look into the people involved

106
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,800
in order to find more clues.

107
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,000
This inspired me.

108
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:05,000
Seeing there was no hope of reversing the case,

109
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:08,280
I colluded with the owner of the Antique Shop.

110
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,720
Using Chen You's burning of the desk,

111
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:15,440
I fabricated the story that Sun Wenhuai escaped to send a letter to Jue Ming,

112
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:19,200
leading you to the Antique Shop to get the suicide note.

113
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,080
Now that I've said it all,

114
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,960
I feel so much lighter.

115
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,760
It was Jueming's words that reminded me.

116
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,760
If you are solving a case,

117
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,320
and right from the start,

118
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,760
you have a hypothetical suspect,

119
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:52,120
then all the clues you investigate

120
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:54,720
will revolve around this idea.

121
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,640
Even the clearest evidence

122
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:00,120
will be ignored.

123
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:04,640
You will create a miscarriage of justice.

124
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,600
Lord Li.

125
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,680
Criminal Su Yu'an

126
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,360
has been waiting for you for a long time.

127
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,160
Su Yu'an.

128
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,360
As an official of the Tang Dynasty,

129
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:36,000
you committed perjury back then.

130
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,000
According to Tang law,

131
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:42,200
based on the provisions regarding perjury and witness statements,

132
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:45,520
if false testimony leads to a wrongful conviction,

133
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:51,320
the punishment shall be reduced by two degrees from the original sentence.

134
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:55,280
Sun Wenhuai was sentenced to death.

135
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,040
A death sentence reduced by two degrees

136
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,360
means exile for 3,000 miles,

137
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:03,120
plus three years of hard labor.

138
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,200
My lord.

139
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,440
My father made a mistake in a moment of confusion.

140
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,880
I am willing to make amends for his crime.

141
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:11,240
Please be lenient, my lord.

142
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,400
Su Lang,

143
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,720
get up.

144
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,320
Father! Father, don't go. Don't go.

145
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,720
It's not like this.

146
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,080
Who is he?

147
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,440
He watched me grow up.

148
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:27,240
He stayed in the yamen his whole life.

149
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,760
He solved countless cases, big and small.

150
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,930
He has made countless contributions.

151
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:34,280
Why did this one case

152
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:37,560
wipe out all his achievements?

153
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,320
But what about the laws of the Tang Dynasty?

154
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,680
Vice Governor Li.

155
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,840
Constable Su turned himself in.

156
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,120
According to Tang Dynasty law,

157
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,720
those who surrender before their crimes are discovered

158
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,580
can be exempted from punishment.

159
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,400
Yes.

160
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,240
Very well.

161
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,160
Get up.

162
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,320
Constable Su.

163
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,600
I,

164
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,280
according to Tang Dynasty law,

165
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,840
will exempt you from all punishments.

166
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,960
But,

167
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,080
this uniform,

168
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,320
you can never wear it again.

169
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:33,240
I, the culprit Su Yu'an.

170
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,920
Thank you, My Lord.

171
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,540
Thank you, My Lord.

172
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,780
Thank you, My Lord.

173
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:51,160
Get up, Lang'er.

174
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,080
Su Lang.

175
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,040
You've grown up.

176
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,800
I actually wanted to take a break a long time ago.

177
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,320
I can't be a constable anymore.

178
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,920
But my son is still a constable.

179
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:15,080
You must enforce the law impartially.

180
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,920
Don't bring shame to me.

181
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,720
You always say I'm a glutton,

182
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:27,480
chewing non-stop every day.

183
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:29,240
Actually, you know what?

184
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,840
Over the years,

185
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:34,760
as soon as my mouth stops,

186
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:39,880
it seems the truth will blurt out.

187
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:46,440
I am relieved now.

188
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,880
Without me in the future,

189
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,360
maybe

190
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,720
Miss Li, you have to be careful.

191
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:02,880
No one will help you lie anymore.

192
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,080
From now on,

193
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,440
you must become a good coroner.

194
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:10,840
Otherwise, you'll have to get married.

195
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,160
Jueming.

196
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:15,000
Yes.

197
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,080
This place,

198
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:19,520
I'll leave it to you.

199
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,120
Yes.

200
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:42,120
This hot pot restaurant is very famous.

201
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,960
Here, try it.

202
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:47,440
This shop is deep inside Hengmen.

203
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,800
When we came, there were few people around,

204
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,200
but it's crowded at the door.

205
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,090
Did your father bring you here?

206
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:59,970
You are amazing, Brother Jueming.

207
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:03,480
The first time my father brought me here

208
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:06,140
was the day I officially became a constable.

209
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:07,920
At that time, we said

210
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:11,140
we would join hands to protect the peace of Luoyang.

211
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,640
Before,

212
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,640
I was always against you.

213
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:20,280
I'm sorry.

214
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,040
I still remember at first,

215
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:26,360
seeing you came from the red-light district,

216
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:29,000
I thought you were just a pretty boy.

217
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:31,580
Later, I saw you solve cases like a god

218
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,680
and crack bizarre mysteries.

219
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:34,720
To be honest,

220
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,560
I was quite jealous.

221
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:41,040
Is this why you treated me to hot pot?

222
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:42,440
Yesterday,

223
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,520
thanks to your righteous words, Brother Jueming,

224
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,720
begging the Deputy Magistrate for leniency,

225
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,850
my father was spared from punishment.

226
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:51,960
Your father

227
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,440
is fair and just,

228
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,760
and abides by the law.

229
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,840
He just had a moment of negligence

230
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,160
and made a mistake.

231
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:02,120
I just did my duty.

232
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,690
Your kindness from yesterday,

233
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:08,040
I, Su Lang, will keep in my heart.

234
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,840
How will you remember it?

235
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:19,720
Boss,

236
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,360
bring another plate of meat.

237
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,040
Coming right up.

238
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,200
And a pot of wine.

239
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,800
Eat more.

240
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:44,760
After eating,

241
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:46,480
let's head back to the yamen.

242
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,720
There are still many cases.

243
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,760
Since your father left,

244
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:50,490
all the cases have fallen on me.

245
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,480
You go back first.

246
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:55,100
I still have some things to do.

247
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,800
These two have started committing crimes again recently.

248
00:14:57,800 --> 00:15:00,120
They don't look like good people. So this is Moya.

249
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,520
Look at the scar on his face.

250
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:04,120
I heard they are a notorious couple of thieves.

251
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,420
Have you seen this person?

252
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,600
No, I haven't.

253
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:19,240
Boss, a steamer of buns and a pot of wine.

254
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:20,320
Okay.

255
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,240
Here are the buns.

256
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,560
Sir, your buns.

257
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,880
Things are so tense right now.

258
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:35,880
I think

259
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:37,780
we can't stay in Luoyang anymore.

260
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,680
Here is the wine you ordered. Enjoy.

261
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:42,080
Okay, thanks.

262
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,120
That female coroner saw your face clearly.

263
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:47,560
You shouldn't have saved her.

264
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:49,000
This is a great taboo in our line of work.

265
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:51,320
If it were me, I would have taken her away.

266
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:53,380
That way, we wouldn't be exposed.

267
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:56,360
We were only after the money,

268
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,920
and we never hurt anyone.

269
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,240
But Dad,

270
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,040
she saw your true face.

271
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,450
Why didn't you kill her?

272
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:10,600
With just the few of them,

273
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:12,680
do you think they can handle me?

274
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:15,680
Do you think I'm that easy to catch?

275
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,000
I'm still worried.

276
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:24,520
The government office is watching us closely now.

277
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:27,000
How about we leave Luoyang?

278
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:34,160
In all my life,

279
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:36,680
I've never been anywhere else.

280
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:40,240
Besides, we've stolen everything worth stealing in Luoyang.

281
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:44,720
Why can't we move somewhere else,

282
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:46,240
buy a big house,

283
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:47,840
and live a good life?

284
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:57,960
Do you really want to leave Luoyang that badly?

285
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:00,200
I just want to live with you, Dad,

286
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,760
and live an ordinary life.

287
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:03,840
Besides,

288
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:06,359
the things we've stolen over the years

289
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:09,020
are enough to last us for several lifetimes.

290
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:14,720
Are you not planning to retire?

291
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,970
Eat the buns first. They're getting cold.

292
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:36,360
Please have some tea.

293
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:38,640
Look at my daughter.

294
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:45,600
Thank you for being lenient with Constable Su this time.

295
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,160
My daughter,

296
00:17:48,520 --> 00:17:50,360
He was at fault first.

297
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,280
His punishment can be spared,

298
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:53,600
but his official position

299
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:55,400
really cannot be kept.

300
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:57,240
However,

301
00:17:58,080 --> 00:17:59,640
I never expected

302
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:02,480
you to solve so many cases all at once.

303
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,680
We still have a bet.

304
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:09,160
Do you mean

305
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:11,210
you want to admit defeat early?

306
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:12,680
How is that possible?

307
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:15,360
The deadline hasn't arrived yet.

308
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:18,720
Although you're doing very well now,

309
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:23,280
I will stick it out until the very end.

310
00:18:24,280 --> 00:18:25,120
Alright then.

311
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,440
When I win,

312
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:27,800
don't regret it.

313
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:28,560
Come, my daughter.

314
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:29,360
Sit down first.

315
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:31,280
Sit down and let me say a few words.

316
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:34,800
Daughter.

317
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:38,160
I'm really worried you won't get married.

318
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:39,720
Think about it.

319
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:41,880
Which gentleman

320
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:45,160
would dare to hold hands that touch corpses every day?

321
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,560
Daughter,

322
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,360
listen to me.

323
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,120
Let's quit.

324
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:54,320
Dad, you dare to touch my hands, don't you?

325
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:59,360
I... I am your father.

326
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:01,600
No, Dad. Those gentlemen you introduced,

327
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:02,360
I don't like them.

328
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:04,160
I don't want to marry them.

329
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:06,800
Who do you want to marry then?

330
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:09,600
You can't stay unmarried for your whole life.

331
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,600
I have my own plans.

332
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,240
I'll go get you some more tea.

333
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,000
Sweetie.

334
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,000
Honglian.

335
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:29,760
Honglian,

336
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:31,760
are you there?

337
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,280
Why are you here today?

338
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:40,080
I didn't put flowers outside.

339
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:41,600
My father is at home today.

340
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,360
There's a performance by the Lu Troupe later.

341
00:19:43,360 --> 00:19:44,400
It's their final show.

342
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:46,960
If we don't watch it now, we'll miss it forever.

343
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:48,760
If my father finds out...

344
00:19:48,840 --> 00:19:49,440
I...

345
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:51,120
It's fine. We'll just come back early.

346
00:19:51,120 --> 00:19:52,600
It'll be fine. Let's go.

347
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:37,200
According to the informant,

348
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,880
the fire at the Qin family's house that day

349
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:43,960
which killed the grandfather, father, mother, second son, and eldest daughter,

350
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:45,360
was unfortunately

351
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,120
an accident.

352
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,480
Coming.

353
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:54,120
Bring more! Put out the fire!

354
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:56,640
Hurry, bring more!

355
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:59,400
Water is here!

356
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:02,920
Bring more water!

357
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:05,960
Hurry, fetch more water!

358
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:06,560
Coming!

359
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:08,600
The fire is big here!

360
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,680
Water is here!

361
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:12,800
Come and help!

362
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,960
Impossible.

363
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,890
This wasn't an accident at all.

364
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,400
This is impossible.

365
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:25,450
What are you talking about?

366
00:21:28,040 --> 00:21:29,040
Nothing.

367
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:31,240
I saw you were all busy,

368
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:33,200
so I came to check some old files.

369
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,000
What did you say wasn't an accident?

370
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:41,280
Look.

371
00:21:41,320 --> 00:21:44,450
The fire at the Qin residence killed five people at once.

372
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:47,280
When the fire just started,

373
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:49,320
didn't they have a chance to escape?

374
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:55,840
That makes sense.

375
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:57,800
But this is just a theory.

376
00:21:57,840 --> 00:21:59,400
You have no evidence.

377
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:08,600
Why are you so interested in the Qin family fire case?

378
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:13,640
I heard Catcher Su talk about Catcher Qin's deeds back then,

379
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:15,640
so I got curious.

380
00:22:24,280 --> 00:22:25,600
Shouldn't you

381
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:27,920
go back with your father?

382
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:30,680
Because I promised Zhen'er

383
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,800
to accompany her to watch the Lu Troupe's performance.

384
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:34,680
I heard this is their last time.

385
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:37,160
They won't perform anymore after this.

386
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:38,840
Come with me.

387
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,200
I still have a lot of case files here.

388
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,480
Let's go. I...

389
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:54,900
Shopkeeper, pack these up and send them to the Guan residence.

390
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,850
Did Master Guan get married again?

391
00:22:57,560 --> 00:23:00,490
This is for the Guan family's little granddaughter.

392
00:23:01,120 --> 00:23:03,640
Master Guan has a granddaughter?

393
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:05,440
Don't ask too many questions.

394
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,760
Pack this up too.

395
00:23:10,080 --> 00:23:11,000
Thank you.

396
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:15,480
The Guan family

397
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:17,040
is quite rich.

398
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:27,440
Wow, how scary.

399
00:23:29,840 --> 00:23:31,520
Aren't you scared?

400
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:32,720
Hold this for her.

401
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:34,680
Let's go look around over there.

402
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:36,400
Look here.

403
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:37,760
Look at this.

404
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:39,000
Do you like anything?

405
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:44,880
You have good taste, Miss.

406
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:52,320
Ladies and gentlemen.

407
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,480
It's starting.

408
00:23:53,520 --> 00:23:54,920
The performance by the Lu Troupe

409
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:55,800
is about to begin!

410
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:56,800
I'll take this first.

411
00:23:56,800 --> 00:23:57,640
Catch it. Alright.

412
00:23:57,640 --> 00:24:00,000
Everyone, don't miss out as you walk by!

413
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:01,440
Excuse me.

414
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:02,680
Excuse me.

415
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:04,560
Thanks.

416
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,080
Excuse me.

417
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:07,920
Here.

418
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,960
Thank you all for your support.

419
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:12,760
Next, my older brother

420
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:14,560
will perform the fire pot show for you.

421
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:17,000
Great!

422
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:18,200
This is the final performance.

423
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,080
This is the Lu Troupe's specialty.

424
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:21,680
Wow, I love watching this.

425
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:23,320
The Lu Troupe is good at this.

426
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:24,120
Look.

427
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:26,520
Coming here today was the right choice.

428
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:34,000
Bravo!

429
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,240
Encore!

430
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,120
How dare you!

431
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,600
Tricking an innocent girl

432
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,520
into coming out to have fun with you.

433
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:59,200
Dad, I wanted to come out and watch it myself.

434
00:25:00,600 --> 00:25:03,530
You're actually doing that money-losing business.

435
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,360
And you,

436
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,800
what do you think you are?

437
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:07,960
A petty constable.

438
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,120
Stay away from my daughter.

439
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:09,440
Get lost!

440
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,080
No.

441
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:11,360
I'll go.

442
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:13,880
Let me tell you, with your meager wages,

443
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,360
trying to trick my Honglian,

444
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:16,720
no way!

445
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,520
Go back.

446
00:25:17,560 --> 00:25:18,560
Encore!

447
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,660
Encore! Look how high the flames are.

448
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:23,320
Great!

449
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:26,360
Mind your status.

450
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,760
Her dad is shortsighted.

451
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,160
You are so young,

452
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,720
with a bright future ahead.

453
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:33,200
You can definitely win her back.

454
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,480
Make him regret it.

455
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:35,440
Listen to me.

456
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,740
Jinglan is over there.

457
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,040
Great!

458
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:45,360
What's wrong?

459
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:46,920
Great!

460
00:25:48,720 --> 00:25:50,320
Great!

461
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:58,520
Encore!

462
00:25:58,560 --> 00:25:59,800
Come on, another one!

463
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,920
Was the previous show exciting?

464
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:07,280
Exciting!

465
00:26:07,320 --> 00:26:08,720
Then, the excitement continues.

466
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,200
Next, our little sister

467
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,960
will bring you the next performance.

468
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,090
Please welcome her.

469
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:15,240
Good.

470
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:19,620
Ladies and gentlemen,

471
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:22,560
did you see the fire dragon dancing in the sky just now?

472
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:24,120
This is a very auspicious sign.

473
00:26:24,120 --> 00:26:27,640
Today, I can grant a wish for someone in the audience.

474
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:30,000
If anyone has a wish in their heart,

475
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:31,370
please raise your hand.

476
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:33,280
Me!

477
00:26:33,320 --> 00:26:35,200
Pick me!

478
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:36,240
Little girl,

479
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:38,320
what is your wish?

480
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:42,400
My mother passed away.

481
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:44,800
I want to see her again.

482
00:26:45,360 --> 00:26:46,320
That's easy.

483
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,320
Watch closely.

484
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:59,120
Our departed loved ones become everything in this world.

485
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,720
Your mother has turned into this flower.

486
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:02,040
Put it by your pillow,

487
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:04,410
and you can see your mother every morning.

488
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:06,360
Thank you.

489
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:15,240
Okay.

490
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,460
Ladies and gentlemen,

491
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:22,040
today is the Lu Troupe's

492
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:24,280
finale performance.

493
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:26,400
We are performing here,

494
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:28,600
thanks to your

495
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:30,320
great support.

496
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:33,800
Next is the grand finale.

497
00:27:34,320 --> 00:27:37,000
Please don't blink.

498
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,200
Watch this.

499
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,800
Everyone, watch closely.

500
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:46,840
Next, I will show you a magic trick.

501
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,160
Please look.

502
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:49,400
This is now an

503
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,920
empty box.

504
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:51,920
Sister.

505
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:56,120
How is this done?

506
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,640
Please look.

507
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:11,920
Wow.

508
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,160
That's amazing.

509
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:15,120
Change her back!

510
00:28:16,360 --> 00:28:17,690
Don't panic, everyone.

511
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:20,200
Now my little sister has turned into a cat.

512
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,160
What's next?

513
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,880
I will turn her back.

514
00:28:23,360 --> 00:28:25,000
The living person illusion!

515
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:36,080
Watch closely, everyone.

516
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,280
Look.

517
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,280
Little sister!

518
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:48,560
Father!

519
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:50,160
So cruel!

520
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:52,800
A murder has occurred.

521
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:53,960
Evacuate the crowd.

